      "d": "Nvidia has dominated the AI chip market for years, but the era of total dependence might be ending.&#160;&#160; OpenAI just shared its plans to spice things up with&#160;Jalapeño, its custom inference chip built with Broadcom, joining Google, Apple, and SpaceX in a growing list of companies building their way out of single-supplier risk. The goal&#160;is&#160;less&#160;of&#160;a [&#8230;]",
